 ans et sa mère, Béatrix D'Ath, avait 36 ans. Il a épousé Mathilde de Boves-Coucy en 1127, à Amiens, Somme, Hauts-de-France, France. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils et 1 fille. Il est décédé en 1147, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 39 ans."},"de":{"1108–1147":"1108–1147","1102–Female":"1102–Verstorben","1104–Male":"1104–Verstorben","1103–1167":"1103–1167","1128–1176":"1128–1176","1145–1204":"1145–1204","1072–1136":"1072–1136","1072–1150":"1072–1150","1176":"1176","1150":"1150","1072":"1072","1128":"1128","1127":"1127","1204":"1204","1104":"1104","1136":"1136","1147":"1147","1103":"1103","1102":"1102","1145":"1145","1167":"1167","1100":"1100","1108":"1108","Amiens, Somme, Picardie, França":"Amiens, Somme, Picardie, Frankreich","Amiens, Somme, Hauts-de-France, France":"Amiens, Somme, Hauts-de-France, Frankreich","France":"Frankreich","lifeSummary":"Als Guy Châtelain d'Amiens 1108 in Amiens, Somme, Picardie, Frankreich geboren wurde, war sein Vater Adam I d'Amiens 36 und seine Mutter Béatrix D'Ath 36. Er hat 1127 in Amiens, Somme, Hauts-de-France, Frankreich Mathilde de Boves-Coucy geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 1 Sohn und 1 Tochter. Er starb 1147 im Alter von 39 Jahren in seinem Geburtsort."},"ht":{"1108–1147":"1108–1147","1102–Female":"1102–Desede","1104–Male":"1104–Desede","1103–1167":"1103–1167","1128–1176":"1128–1176","1145–1204":"1145–1204","1072–1136":"1072–1136","1072–1150":"1072–1150","1176":"1176","1150":"1150","1072":"1072","1128":"1128","1127":"1127","1204":"1204","1104":"1104","1136":"1136","1147":"1147","1103":"1103","1102":"1102","1145":"1145","1167":"1167","1100":"1100","1108":"1108","Amiens, Somme, Picardie, França":"Amiens, Somme, Picardie, France","Amiens, Somme, Hauts-de-France, France":"Amiens, Somme, Hauts-de-France, France","France":"France"},"hu":{"1108–1147":"1108–1147","1102–Female":"1102–elhunyt","1104–Male":"1104–elhunyt","1103–1167":"1103–1167","1128–1176":"1128–1176","1145–1204":"1145–1204","1072–1136":"1072–1136","1072–1150":"1072–1150","1